{
  "id": "adv_event_2602_01_05_02",
  "title": "ハッピーバレンタイン！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、一味違う私達の姿、いかがでしたか？\nそしてここでサプラーイズ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8057117762,
      "endTime": 10.0882519069,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13937.842018899999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 5.1666393257
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 6.8333059049
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
      "startTime": 8.8999983119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "伊吹渚プレゼンツ！\n『胸キュン告白選手権Z』を開催します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2839660626,
      "endTime": 15.843966291500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.0396804474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "メンバーが愛の告白をするなら……どんな風になるのか\n私がイメージをして台詞を書き下ろしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.0396804474,
      "endTime": 24.7377526902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.933466846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "来てくれたみんなに甘い告白をお届けしますねっ！\nまずは芽衣ちゃんからどうぞー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.933466846,
      "endTime": 32.4739658656,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6087.2127606
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.636330412
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.8363395673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！　君のためにチョコドーナツたーっくさん\n作ってきたんだよ～！　一緒に食べよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6363395673,
      "endTime": 43.4363395674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "君と食べるドーナツはいつもより甘いな～\n芽衣、君と過ごす時間が、一番のお気に入りだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6320537232,
      "endTime": 55.1535751008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.3611148182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、君と一緒にいつまでもいたいって思ってるんだ\nこの気持ち、君が教えてくれたよね。大好きだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3611148182,
      "endTime": 69.4887563053,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13938.896893699997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.6844704611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～！　あどけなさを感じさせつつもなんて素直で\n大胆な告白！　ふふ、お次は沙季ちゃーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6844704611,
      "endTime": 80.6743794425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.8034177763
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 82.036768403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "その、私、恋愛というものには大変疎くて……\nそれでも、あなたと会えない時間がとても辛いんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.836768403,
      "endTime": 93.7710543298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "辛くて寂しいのに……あなたのことばかり考えてしまう\nこのチョコを作った時だって、ずっと考えていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9667684857,
      "endTime": 103.6081066435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 103.8038207992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "おそらくこれが、恋……初めての恋なんだと思います\n大好きです。私の想い、受け取ってくれますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8038207992,
      "endTime": 115.7377433761,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11596.190912700009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 115.933457532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "く～！　ぎこちなさや戸惑い混じりだけど\n想いが伝わりましたね！　次は～すずちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.933457532,
      "endTime": 125.1183099414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 126.2473401373
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 126.480698902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "さぁどうぞ、感謝なさい。これは有名パティシエの\n高級チョコで――って、こ、ここで開けるんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.280698902,
      "endTime": 137.80614083470002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、不出来でしょう。当然ですわ\nだって本当は私の手作りですから。な、なんでって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0140322353,
      "endTime": 150.80967871209998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 151.0140322353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "て、手作りを食べてほしいからに決まっていますわ\n私にとってあなたは特別ですもの……好き、なのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0140322353,
      "endTime": 164.9239927913,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13285.979476600005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 165.1140383388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、ちょっぴり素直じゃないとこがまた\nキュンときますね～！　そして次は～琴乃ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.1140383388,
      "endTime": 174.74263254669998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 175.8716546044
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 176.1050215072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと……この気持ちに気付けなかったの\n私にとっていつも隣にいることが、当たり前だったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.9050215072,
      "endTime": 185.8333450452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "あなたが傍にいるだけで、毎日が輝いてる\nあなたが傍にいてくれるから、私は寂しくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.0716861393,
      "endTime": 195.4409381534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 195.7716841048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、この当たり前にもう甘えない\nこのチョコと一緒に伝えるわ。あなたのことが、大好き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.7716841048,
      "endTime": 205.5433389968,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9361.660940400014
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 205.7383507714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_05-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "こ、琴乃ちゅわぁん……国宝級の告白だよ！\nあぁ、どうして録音してなかったの、私！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.7383507714,
      "endTime": 216.88835115290001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.6905482
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 217.0840653088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
